"tassa, bhikkhave, hoti dīgharattaṃ ahitāya dukkhāya kāyassa bhedā paraṃ "
"maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapajjati. (2)"
msgstr ""

