msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.72:9.3"
msgid "“Etadeva, bhante, varaṃ—yaṃ khattiyamahāsālānaṃ vā … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.72:9.4"
msgid ""
"saddhādeyyaṃ cīvaraṃ paribhuñjeyya, dukkhañhetaṃ, bhante, yaṃ balavā puriso "
"tattena ayopaṭṭena ādittena sampajjalitena sajotibhūtena kāyaṃ "
"sampaliveṭheyyā”ti."
